description: Cabernet`s Oshawott was seen in a flashback scene when Cabernet was explaining her first battling experience with Cilan at the Sanyo Gym. Cabernet`s Oshawott was defeated by Cilan`s Pansage and Cabernet made is seem like Cilan and Cilan`s Pansage were manically monsters for defeating Cabernet`s Oshawott.
name: Mijumaru (Cabernet)
